thread.title: BLAIR, PATRICIA

author: BLAIR, PATRICIA
title: BLAIR, PATRICIA
text:
Excellent Company! I highly recommend Whole Latte Love Company.
I am greatly enjoying the espresso machine I bought from them and the coffee they included with the purchase. I don't go to Starbucks anymore!
I can have my espresso any time I want it, I don't have to wait in line, and I don't have to hope the barista gets my order correct! Yeah! I'm HAPPY!
